<section>

    <h2>What is SUEP?</h2>

    <p>SUEP (Self-Sustaining Urban Energy Pod) is a revolutionary clean energy system that generates and distributes electricity using solar power, kinetic energy, and smart AI-driven management.</p>

</section>



<section>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>

    <div class="features">

        <div class="feature-box">

            <h3>Solar Energy</h3>

            <p>Captures and stores sunlight using ultra-efficient solar panels.</p>

        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">

            <h3>Kinetic Energy</h3>

            <p>Harvests energy from footsteps and movement to generate power.</p>

        </div>

        <div class="feature-box">

            <h3>Wireless Sharing</h3>

            <p>Distributes excess power to homes and businesses seamlessly.</p>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>



